# A complete chat server in 10 declarative lines.
# Every keyword is an ABSTRACT verb — never a target-language
# literal — so the same source survives if you swap the library to
# Node, Python, Rust, etc. The library decides what each verb
# compiles to.

server "8080"
route "/chat"

field chat user string
field chat text string

field join user string

on chat broadcast
on join announce
end
